org.researchstack.skin

Class ResearchStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.researchstack.skin.ResearchStack

  • public abstract class ResearchStack
extends java.lang.Object
    Research stack is a singleton which controls all the major components of the ResearchStack framework. It is best to initialize within your Apps Application.onCreate() method.
